<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: 'API Keys' }) %></head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-6 px-4 py-8">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">API Keys</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Kelola kunci akses REST API untuk bot / aplikasimu.</p>
    </div>

    <% if (flash) { %>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-amber-200"><%= flash %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/apikeys" class="card flex flex-wrap gap-3 p-4">
      <input name="label" placeholder="Label, mis. bot-telegram-prod" class="input flex-1" required />
      <button class="btn btn-primary">Buat API Key</button>
    </form>

    <section class="card overflow-hidden">
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="text-left text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">
              <th class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Label</th>
              <th class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Public Key</th>
              <th class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Secret</th>
              <th class="px-5 py-3 font-medium">Status</th>
              <th class="px-5 py-3 font-medium"></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5">
            <% keys.forEach(function (k) { %>
              <tr class="transition hover:bg-white/[0.03]">
                <td class="px-5 py-3 text-slate-200"><%= k.label %></td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-brand-300"><%= k.key %></td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-slate-500"><%= k.secret.slice(0, 6) %>…<%= k.secret.slice(-4) %></td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">
                  <span class="badge <%= k.isActive ? 'badge-paid' : 'badge-expired' %>"><%= k.isActive ? 'AKTIF' : 'NONAKTIF' %></span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                    <form method="POST" action="/apikeys/<%= k.id %>/toggle"><button class="text-xs text-slate-400 hover:text-white">Toggle</button></form>
                    <form method="POST" action="/apikeys/<%= k.id %>/delete" onsubmit="return confirm('Hapus API key ini?')"><button class="text-xs text-rose-400 hover:text-rose-300">Hapus</button></form>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
            <% if (!keys.length) { %>
              <tr><td class="px-5 py-10 text-center text-slate-500" colspan="5">Belum ada API key.</td></tr>
            <% } %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =================================================================== -->
    <!-- API DOCUMENTATION                                                    -->
    <!-- =================================================================== -->
    <section class="card space-y-8 p-6" id="docs">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">API Documentation</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Semua yang perlu untuk integrasi ke bot Telegram / aplikasimu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/60 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs">
          <div class="text-slate-500">Base URL</div>
          <span class="text-brand-300" id="baseUrlDisplay"><%= baseUrl %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Auth -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">1. Authentication</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Setiap request ke <code class="rounded bg-white/10 px-1 text-brand-300">/api/v1/*</code> wajib menyertakan header
          <code class="rounded bg-white/10 px-1 text-brand-300">X-API-Key</code> berisi <em>public key</em>-mu (diawali <code>pk_</code>).
        </p>
        <pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>X-API-Key: pk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</code></pre>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">
          <em>Secret key</em> (<code>sk_</code>) TIDAK dipakai di request — dia dipakai server untuk sign webhook (HMAC-SHA256)
          supaya botmu bisa verifikasi webhook itu asli.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Endpoints -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">2. Endpoints</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-sm">

          <!-- Create invoice -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-500/15 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-emerald-200">
              <span class="rounded bg-emerald-500/30 px-2 py-0.5">POST</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-emerald-300/80">Buat invoice baru</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Request body (JSON)</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>{
  "amount": 1000,                          // WAJIB. Integer rupiah, tanpa unique code.
  "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",              // OPSIONAL. Kalau kosong, auto jadi "KCS-XXXXXXXX".
  "description": "Beli topup 1rb",         // OPSIONAL.
  "callback_url": "https://mybot/hook",    // OPSIONAL. Webhook saat invoice PAID.
  "provider_id": 1                         // OPSIONAL. Default: provider aktif pertama.
}</code></pre>
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Response 200 OK</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>{
  "reference":         "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",     // ID public. Simpan ini!
  "merchant_ref":      "ORDER-42",           // Ref-mu, atau "KCS-XXXXXXXX" bila auto-generate
  "amount":            1000,                 // Nominal asli
  "unique_code":       342,                  // 1-999, ditambahkan biar unik
  "total_amount":      1342,                 // Nominal YANG HARUS DIBAYAR
  "status":            "PENDING",
  "qris_string":       "00020101021226...",  // Bisa di-render sendiri jadi QR
  "qris_image":        "data:image/png;base64,...", // PNG siap pakai
  "expired_at":        "2026-07-23T05:00:00.000Z",
  "pay_url":           "<%= baseUrl %>/pay/INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "idempotent_replay": false                 // true = invoice existing dikembalikan
}</code></pre>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-500/25 bg-amber-500/10 p-3 text-xs text-amber-100">
                <div class="mb-1 font-semibold">Idempotency via <code>merchant_ref</code></div>
                Kalau kamu retry POST dengan <code>merchant_ref</code> yang SAMA (mis. bot timeout &amp; retry),
                request kedua <strong>tidak</strong> bikin invoice baru — kita balikin invoice PENDING yang sama.
                Header response berisi <code class="rounded bg-white/10 px-1">X-Idempotent-Replay: true</code>
                dan field <code>idempotent_replay: true</code>.
                <div class="mt-1">
                  Kalau <code>merchant_ref</code> sama tapi <code>amount</code> beda → ditolak HTTP 409
                  (<code>merchant_ref_conflict</code>).
                </div>
                <div class="mt-1">
                  <strong>Catatan:</strong> kalau kamu <em>tidak</em> mengirim <code>merchant_ref</code>, sistem
                  membuatkan ref acak <code>KCS-XXXXXXXX</code> otomatis. Karena selalu unik, ref auto ini
                  tidak ikut logika idempotency — tiap POST tanpa <code>merchant_ref</code> = invoice baru.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Get invoice -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-sky-500/15 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-sky-200">
              <span class="rounded bg-sky-500/30 px-2 py-0.5">GET</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices/:reference</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-sky-300/80">Cek status invoice</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 p-3">
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Response 200 OK</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>{
  "reference":    "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",
  "amount":       1000,
  "unique_code":  342,
  "total_amount": 1342,
  "status":       "PAID",                    // PENDING | PAID | EXPIRED | CANCELLED
  "paid_at":      "2026-07-23T04:05:12.000Z",
  "expired_at":   "2026-07-23T05:00:00.000Z",
  "pay_url":      "<%= baseUrl %>/pay/INV-XXXXXXXXXX"
}</code></pre>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">
                Bot bisa poll tiap 3-5 detik sampai status berubah. Alternatif lebih hemat: pakai webhook.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cancel invoice -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-rose-500/15 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-rose-200">
              <span class="rounded bg-rose-500/30 px-2 py-0.5">POST</span>
              <span>/api/v1/invoices/:reference/cancel</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-rose-300/80">Batalkan invoice PENDING</span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 p-3">
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>{ "ok": true }</code></pre>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Hanya bisa cancel invoice yang statusnya masih <code>PENDING</code>.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Webhook -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">3. Webhook (opsional, direkomendasikan)</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400">
          Kalau kamu isi <code>callback_url</code>, PG akan POST payload berikut <strong>begitu invoice jadi PAID</strong>.
          Retry 3× jeda 2 detik kalau responsemu non-2xx.
        </p>
<pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>Headers:
  Content-Type: application/json
  X-Event:      invoice.paid
  X-Signature:  HMAC-SHA256(rawBody, apiKey.secret)   // hex-encoded

Body:
{
  "event":        "invoice.paid",
  "reference":    "INV-XXXXXXXXXX",
  "merchantRef":  "ORDER-42",
  "amount":       1000,
  "uniqueCode":   342,
  "totalAmount":  1342,
  "status":       "PAID",
  "paidAt":       "2026-07-23T04:05:12.000Z",
  "providerType": "orderkuota_jywa"
}</code></pre>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Verify di sisi bot (Python):</p>
<pre class="mt-1 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>import hmac, hashlib
expected = hmac.new(SECRET.encode(), raw_body, hashlib.sha256).hexdigest()
if expected != request.headers.get("X-Signature"):
    return 401</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Error codes -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">4. Error responses</h3>
        <div class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10">
          <table class="w-full text-xs">
            <thead class="bg-white/5 text-slate-400">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">HTTP</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">error code</th>
                <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Kenapa &amp; cara handle di bot</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5">
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">401</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">missing_api_key / invalid_api_key</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Header X-API-Key salah / kosong / nonaktif.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">400</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">invalid_amount</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Amount bukan integer positif atau &gt; 9.999.000.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">400</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">provider_not_found / provider_inactive</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400"><code>provider_id</code> tidak ada / non-aktif.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">400</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">no_active_provider</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Belum ada Provider aktif di dashboard.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">400</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">bad_request</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Body JSON invalid / field wajib kosong.</td></tr>
              <tr class="bg-amber-500/5"><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-amber-200">409</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-amber-200">merchant_ref_conflict</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400"><code>merchant_ref</code> sudah dipakai invoice PENDING lain dengan amount berbeda.</td></tr>
              <tr class="bg-amber-500/5"><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-amber-200">429</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-amber-200">unique_code_pool_exhausted</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">&gt; 999 invoice PENDING dgn amount sama. Response berisi header <code>Retry-After: 10</code>. Bot: sleep 10 detik lalu retry.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">404</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">not_found</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Reference invoice tidak ditemukan.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">403</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">forbidden</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">API key ini bukan pemilik invoice tsb.</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">400</td><td class="px-3 py-2 font-mono text-slate-300">invalid_state</td><td class="px-3 py-2 text-slate-400">Cancel dipanggil ke invoice non-PENDING.</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Code examples -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">5. Contoh Kode</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 overflow-x-auto border-b border-white/10 text-xs">
          <button data-tab="curl" class="tab-btn border-b-2 border-brand-400 px-3 py-2 font-semibold text-white">cURL</button>
          <button data-tab="python" class="tab-btn border-b-2 border-transparent px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-white">Python (requests)</button>
          <button data-tab="pyTelegramBot" class="tab-btn whitespace-nowrap border-b-2 border-transparent px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-white">Bot Telegram (Python)</button>
          <button data-tab="node" class="tab-btn border-b-2 border-transparent px-3 py-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-white">Node.js (axios)</button>
        </div>

        <!-- cURL -->
        <div class="tab-panel" data-tab="curl">
          <div class="mb-1 mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Buat invoice</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>curl -X POST <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"amount": 1000, "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42", "description": "Test"}'</code></pre>
          <div class="mb-1 mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Cek status</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>curl <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices/INV-XXXXXXXXXX \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"</code></pre>
          <div class="mb-1 mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Cancel</div>
<pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>curl -X POST <%= baseUrl %>/api/v1/invoices/INV-XXXXXXXXXX/cancel \
  -H "X-API-Key: pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"</code></pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Python -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="python">
<pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>import requests

BASE = "<%= baseUrl %>"
KEY  = "pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"
H    = {"X-API-Key": KEY, "Content-Type": "application/json"}

# 1. Buat invoice
r = requests.post(f"{BASE}/api/v1/invoices", headers=H, json={
    "amount":       1000,
    "merchant_ref": "ORDER-42",
    "description":  "Test dari Python",
})
r.raise_for_status()
inv = r.json()
print("Reference:", inv["reference"])
print("Bayar Rp", inv["total_amount"])
print("Pay URL :", inv["pay_url"])

# 2. Simpan QRIS jadi file PNG
import base64
png_b64 = inv["qris_image"].split(",", 1)[1]
with open("qris.png", "wb") as f:
    f.write(base64.b64decode(png_b64))

# 3. Poll status tiap 3 detik sampai PAID atau EXPIRED
import time
while True:
    s = requests.get(f"{BASE}/api/v1/invoices/{inv['reference']}", headers=H).json()
    print("Status:", s["status"])
    if s["status"] in ("PAID", "EXPIRED", "CANCELLED"):
        break
    time.sleep(3)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Python Telegram Bot -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="pyTelegramBot">
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Contoh minimal pakai
            <a class="link" href="https://github.com/python-telegram-bot/python-telegram-bot" target="_blank">python-telegram-bot</a>
            v20+.
          </p>
<pre class="mt-2 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>import asyncio, base64, io, requests
from telegram import Update, InputFile
from telegram.ext import Application, CommandHandler, ContextTypes

PG_BASE    = "<%= baseUrl %>"
PG_API_KEY = "pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE"
BOT_TOKEN  = "1234567:AAxxxx"        # dari @BotFather

def create_invoice(amount: int, chat_id: int, order_id: str) -> dict:
    r = requests.post(
        f"{PG_BASE}/api/v1/invoices",
        headers={"X-API-Key": PG_API_KEY, "Content-Type": "application/json"},
        json={
            "amount":       amount,
            "merchant_ref": f"TG-{chat_id}-{order_id}",
            "description":  f"Order dari Telegram chat {chat_id}",
        },
        timeout=15,
    )
    if r.status_code == 429:
        import time
        time.sleep(int(r.headers.get("Retry-After", "10")))
        return create_invoice(amount, chat_id, order_id)
    r.raise_for_status()
    return r.json()

async def buy(update: Update, ctx: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    if not ctx.args:
        return await update.message.reply_text("Usage: /buy &lt;amount&gt;")
    amount   = int(ctx.args[0])
    chat_id  = update.effective_chat.id
    order_id = str(update.message.message_id)
    inv      = create_invoice(amount, chat_id, order_id)

    png = base64.b64decode(inv["qris_image"].split(",", 1)[1])
    caption = (
        f"Bayar sebesar Rp {inv['total_amount']:,}\n"
        f"Reference: {inv['reference']}\n"
        f"Expired: {inv['expired_at']}"
    )
    await update.message.reply_photo(
        photo=InputFile(io.BytesIO(png), filename="qris.png"),
        caption=caption,
    )
    asyncio.create_task(watch_invoice(ctx, chat_id, inv["reference"]))

async def watch_invoice(ctx, chat_id, reference):
    for _ in range(300):
        await asyncio.sleep(3)
        s = requests.get(
            f"{PG_BASE}/api/v1/invoices/{reference}",
            headers={"X-API-Key": PG_API_KEY}, timeout=10,
        ).json()
        if s["status"] == "PAID":
            await ctx.bot.send_message(chat_id, f"Pembayaran {reference} DITERIMA!")
            return
        if s["status"] in ("EXPIRED", "CANCELLED"):
            await ctx.bot.send_message(chat_id, f"Invoice {reference} {s['status']}")
            return

app = Application.builder().token(BOT_TOKEN).build()
app.add_handler(CommandHandler("buy", buy))
app.run_polling()</code></pre>
        </div>

        <!-- Node.js -->
        <div class="tab-panel hidden" data-tab="node">
<pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900/70 p-3 text-xs text-slate-200"><code>const axios = require('axios');

const pg = axios.create({
  baseURL: '<%= baseUrl %>/api/v1',
  headers: { 'X-API-Key': 'pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE' },
});

async function main() {
  const { data: inv } = await pg.post('/invoices', {
    amount:       1000,
    merchant_ref: 'ORDER-42',
    description:  'Test dari Node.js',
  });
  console.log('Reference:', inv.reference);
  console.log('Bayar Rp', inv.total_amount);

  while (true) {
    await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 3000));
    const { data: s } = await pg.get(`/invoices/${inv.reference}`);
    console.log('Status:', s.status);
    if (['PAID', 'EXPIRED', 'CANCELLED'].includes(s.status)) break;
  }
}

main().catch(console.error);</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Notes -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-400/20 bg-brand-500/5 p-4 text-xs text-slate-300">
        <div class="mb-1 font-semibold text-brand-300">Konsep &amp; batasan yang perlu dipahami</div>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5">
          <li><strong>Matching pembayaran:</strong> QRIS dari bank / OrderKuota tidak membawa <code>merchant_ref</code>.
            Yang muncul di mutasi cuma nominal. Jadi tiap invoice ditambahi <code>unique_code</code> 1-999 rupiah — user bayar
            <code>total_amount</code>, bukan <code>amount</code>.</li>
          <li><strong>Idempotency:</strong> kirim <code>merchant_ref</code> sendiri kalau butuh retry aman.
            Tanpa <code>merchant_ref</code>, sistem auto-generate <code>KCS-XXXXXXXX</code> dan tiap POST bikin invoice baru.</li>
          <li><strong>Race-safe:</strong> pemilihan <code>unique_code</code> + insert Invoice diserialisasi dalam satu DB transaction.</li>
          <li><strong>Pool <code>unique_code</code> maks. 999 per amount.</strong> Kalau habis → HTTP 429. Bot: sleep sesuai
            <code>Retry-After</code> lalu retry, atau varietasikan amount.</li>
          <li><strong>Poller</strong> jalan ~10 detik sekali. Invoice expire default 15 menit (<code>INVOICE_EXPIRE_MINUTES</code>).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(function (btn) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        const t = btn.dataset.tab;
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(function (b) {
          const active = b.dataset.tab === t;
          b.classList.toggle('border-brand-400', active);
          b.classList.toggle('text-white', active);
          b.classList.toggle('font-semibold', active);
          b.classList.toggle('border-transparent', !active);
          b.classList.toggle('text-slate-500', !active);
        });
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel').forEach(function (p) {
          p.classList.toggle('hidden', p.dataset.tab !== t);
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
